René Alexandre https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ren%C3%A9_Alexandre 0 René Alexandre (22 December 1885 – 19 August 1946) was a French actor. René Alexandre was born in Reims and died in Vitré, Ille-et-Vilaine in 1946. He was married to actress Gabrielle Robinne in from 1912 until his death.
